W LR copied to Muon without adjust_lr_fn or retuning", "no optimizer comparison against undertuned AdamW baseline"], "cpu_lpddr5x_MB": 491520, "cpu_lpddr5x_bandwidth_GBps": 500, "gpu_hbm3_bandwidth_GBps": 4000, "l2_cache_MB_per_core": 1, "fp8_tflops": 1979, "fp16_tflops": 990, "bf16_tflops": 990, "tf32_tflops": 494, "tflops_note": "dense TFLOPS; ~2x with Sparsity", "source_url": "https://docs.nvidia.com/grace-perf-tuning-guide/index.html"}');
