ives", "no CUDA extension missing sm_90", "no FP8 default without accuracy validation", "no hard-coded job VRAM cap", "no Muon for embedding/bias/norm/head/non-2D params", "no AdamW LR copied to Muon without adjust_lr_fn or retuning", "no optimizer comparison against undertuned AdamW baseline"], "memory_bandwidth_GBps": 3350, "int8_tops": 3958, "fp8_tflops": 3958, "fp16_tflops": 1979, "bf16_tflops": 1979, "tf32_tflops": 989, "tflops_note": "with Sparsity", "source_url": "https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/data-center/h100/"}');
